---
title: SuperQuick Chorizo and Black Bean Nachos  with Guac and Creamy Dressing
description: These super-quick chorizo nachos are ready in just 15 minutes! For this flavour fiesta, crispy tortilla chips are loaded with spicy chorizo and gooey melted cheese, then topped with tangy sour cream, fresh guacamole and a sprinkle of green onions.

